    "Additional details relating to deployment appear in Appendix A.",
    "To demonstrate PoLAR's effectiveness at scale, we fine-tune backbones spanning 350M-27B parameters on three benchmarks of varying difficulty.",
    "Our study includes both masked and autoregressive language models and evaluates their abilities in terms of general language understanding, commonsense reasoning, and multi-step mathematical problem solving.",
    "Commonsense reasoning tasks aim to assess how well LLMs can mimic human-like understanding.",
    "A standard suite of eight different datasets is chosen, and LLMs are finetuned separately on each of the datasets."
